Name: sam2matrix
Author: Jochen Singer <jochen.singer@fu-berlin.de>
Maintainer: Jochen Singer <jochen.singer@fu-berlin.de>
License: GPL v3
Copyright: 2008-2014, FU Berlin
Status: under development
Description: This program determines for each read in the reference file if it
 has an entry in the provided sam files stating that it mapped.
 .
  The generated ouput file contains the number of references and the
  number of reads in the first line. The next line contain the names of
  the references used in the sam files. Afterwards for each read a line
  is creating containing the ids of the references the read mapped to.
